üëâ Think of it like: ‚ÄúBCL + Extra features.‚Äù
It‚Äôs a bigger library that includes:

ASP.NET

ADO.NET

Windows Forms

WCF, WPF


In project:
You use ASP.NET Core for your web APIs ‚Äî it‚Äôs part of FCL.


